#: globals.php:2355 globals.php:2358 site/course/course-content.php:87
#: site/course/course-content.php:102 site/course/course-content.php:111
#: site/course/course-content.php:372 site/course/course-content.php:3332
#: site/course/course-content.php:3350 site/pages/follow-jesus.php:177
msgid "God Uses Ordinary People"
msgstr "Tuhan Guna Orang Biasa"

#: globals.php:2357 site/pages/follow-jesus.php:178
msgid ""
"You'll see how God uses ordinary people doing simple things to make a big "
"impact."
msgstr ""
"Anda akan melihat bagaimana Tuhan menggunakan orang biasa yang melakukan "
"perkara mudah untuk memberikan impak yang besar."

#: globals.php:2368 site/course/course-content.php:3333
#: site/course/course-content.php:3351 site/pages/follow-jesus.php:181
msgid "Simple Definition of Disciple and Church"
msgstr "Definisi Ringkas bagi Murid dan Gereja"

#: globals.php:2370 site/course/course-content.php:157
#: site/pages/follow-jesus.php:182
msgid ""
"Discover the essence of being a disciple, making a disciple, and what is the "
"church."
msgstr ""
"Temui intipati sebenar tentang apa itu menjadi seorang murid, cara "
"pemuridan, dan apakah itu gereja."

#: globals.php:2371 site/course/course-content.php:147
#: site/course/course-content.php:156
msgid "Disciples and the Church"
msgstr "Murid dan Gereja"

#: globals.php:2381 site/course/course-content.php:3334
#: site/course/course-content.php:3352 site/pages/follow-jesus.php:203
msgid "Spiritual Breathing is Hearing and Obeying God"
msgstr "Pernafasan Rohani adalah Mendengar dan Mentaati Tuhan"

#: globals.php:2383 site/pages/follow-jesus.php:204
msgid "Being a disciple means we hear from God and we obey God."
msgstr ""
"Menjadi seorang murid bermaksud kita mendengar daripada Tuhan dan kita "
"mentaati Tuhan."

#: globals.php:2384 site/course/course-content.php:196
#: site/course/course-content.php:205
msgid "Hearing and Obeying God"
msgstr "Mendengar dan Mentaati Tuhan"

#: globals.php:2394 globals.php:2397
msgid "S.O.A.P.S. Bible Study"
msgstr "S.O.A.P.S. Kajian Alkitab"

#: globals.php:2396 site/pages/follow-jesus.php:219
msgid ""
"A tool for daily Bible study that helps you understand, obey, and share "
"God’s Word."
msgstr ""
"Satu alat untuk kajian Alkitab harian yang membantu anda memahami, mentaati, "
"dan berkongsi Firman Tuhan."

#: globals.php:2407 globals.php:2410 site/course/course-content.php:94
#: site/course/course-content.php:307 site/course/course-content.php:316
#: site/course/course-content.php:379 site/course/course-content.php:3581
#: site/course/course-content.php:3597 site/pages/follow-jesus.php:233
msgid "Accountability Groups"
msgstr "Kumpulan Pertanggungjawaban"

#: globals.php:2409 site/pages/follow-jesus.php:234
msgid ""
"A tool for two or three people of the same gender to meet weekly and "
"encourage each other in areas that are going well and reveal areas that need "
"correction."
msgstr ""
"Satu alat untuk dua atau tiga orang yang sama jantina untuk bertemu setiap "
"minggu bagi memberi sokongan dalam perkara yang berjalan lancar dan "
"mendedahkan bahagian yang memerlukan pembetulan."

#: globals.php:2420 site/pages/follow-jesus.php:197
msgid "Consumer vs Producer Lifestyle"
msgstr "Gaya Hidup Pengguna dan Pengeluar"

#: globals.php:2422 site/pages/follow-jesus.php:198
msgid ""
"You'll discover the four main ways God makes everyday followers more like "
"Jesus."
msgstr ""
"Anda akan menemui empat cara utama bagaimana Tuhan membentuk pengikut biasa "
"menjadi lebih menyerupai Yesus."

#: globals.php:2423
msgid "Producer not Consumer"
msgstr "Pengeluar, bukan Pengguna"

#: globals.php:2433 globals.php:2436 site/pages/follow-jesus.php:207
msgid "How to Spend an Hour in Prayer"
msgstr "Cara Meluangkan Satu Jam dalam Doa"

#: globals.php:2435 site/pages/follow-jesus.php:208
msgid "See how easy it is to spend an hour in prayer."
msgstr "Lihat betapa mudahnya untuk meluangkan masa satu jam dalam doa."

#: globals.php:2446 site/pages/follow-jesus.php:294
msgid "Relational Stewardship – List of 100"
msgstr "Penatalayanan Hubungan – Senarai 100"

#: globals.php:2448 site/pages/follow-jesus.php:295
msgid "A tool designed to help you be a good steward of your relationships."
msgstr ""
"Satu alat yang direka untuk membantu anda menjadi penatalayan yang baik bagi "
"hubungan-hubungan anda."

#: globals.php:2449 site/activities/list-of-100-printable.php:22
#: site/activities/list-of-100-printable.php:90
#: site/activities/list-of-100.php:22 site/activities/list-of-100.php:81
#: site/course/course-content.php:496 site/course/course-content.php:634
#: site/course/course-content.php:643 site/course/course-content.php:707
#: site/course/course-content.php:3707 site/course/course-content.php:3727
#: utilities/integrations/replace-placeholder.php:98
#: utilities/integrations/replace-placeholder.php:99
#: utilities/integrations/replace-placeholder.php:100
msgid "List of 100"
msgstr "Senarai 100"

#: globals.php:2459 globals.php:2462 site/course/course-content.php:832
#: site/course/course-content.php:845 site/course/course-content.php:854
#: site/course/course-content.php:3977 site/course/course-content.php:3996
msgid "Spiritual Economy"
msgstr "Ekonomi Rohani"

#: globals.php:2461 site/pages/follow-jesus.php:253
msgid ""
"Learn how God's economy is different from the world's. God invests more in "
"those who are faithful with what they've already been given."
msgstr ""
"Pelajari bagaimana ekonomi Tuhan sangat berbeza daripada ekonomi dunia. "
"Tuhan melabur lebih banyak kepada mereka yang setia dengan apa yang telah "
"diberikan kepada mereka."

#: globals.php:2472 site/pages/follow-jesus.php:298
msgid "The Gospel and How to Share It"
msgstr "Injil dan Cara Mengongsikannya"

#: globals.php:2474 site/pages/follow-jesus.php:299
msgid ""
"Learn a way to share God’s Good News from the beginning of humanity all the "
"way to the end of this age."
msgstr ""
"Pelajari satu cara untuk mengongsikan Berita Baik Tuhan bermula dari "
"penciptaan manusia sehinggalah ke akhir zaman."

#: globals.php:2475
msgid "Sharing God‘s Story"
msgstr "Berkongsi Kisah Tuhan"

#: globals.php:2485 site/pages/follow-jesus.php:245
msgid "Baptism and How To Do It"
msgstr "Pembaptisan dan Cara Melakukannya"

#: globals.php:2487 site/pages/follow-jesus.php:246
msgid ""
"Jesus said, “Go and make disciples of all nations, BAPTIZING them in the "
"name of the Father and of the Son and of the Holy Spirit…” Learn how to put "
"this into practice."
msgstr ""
"Yesus berkata, “Pergilah dan jadikanlah semua bangsa murid-Ku, BAPTISLAH "
"mereka dalam nama Bapa, Anak, dan Roh Kudus…” Pelajarilah bagaimana untuk "
"mempraktikkan perintah ini."

#: globals.php:2488 site/course/course-content.php:837
#: site/course/course-content.php:1043 site/course/course-content.php:1052
#: site/course/course-content.php:1118 site/course/course-content.php:4252
#: site/course/course-content.php:4269
msgid "Baptism"
msgstr "Pembaptisan"

#: globals.php:2498 site/pages/follow-jesus.php:302
msgid "Prepare Your 3-Minute Testimony"
msgstr "Sediakan Kesaksian 3 Minit anda"

#: globals.php:2500 site/pages/follow-jesus.php:303
msgid ""
"Learn how to share your testimony in three minutes by sharing how Jesus has "
"impacted your life."
msgstr ""
"Pelajari cara untuk mengongsikan kesaksian anda dalam masa tiga minit dengan "
"menceritakan bagaimana Yesus telah memberikan impak dalam hidup anda."

#: globals.php:2501
msgid "3-Minute Testimony"
msgstr "Kesaksian 3 Minit"

#: globals.php:2511 site/course/course-content.php:1237
#: site/course/course-content.php:1518 site/course/course-content.php:3978
#: site/course/course-content.php:3997 site/pages/follow-jesus.php:185
msgid "Vision Casting the Greatest Blessing"
msgstr "Visi: Berkat Terbesar"

#: globals.php:2513 site/course/course-content.php:1318
#: site/pages/follow-jesus.php:186
msgid ""
"Learn a simple pattern of making not just one follower of Jesus but entire "
"spiritual families who multiply for generations to come."
msgstr ""
"Pelajari satu corak mudah untuk melahirkan bukan sekadar seorang pengikut "
"Yesus, tetapi seluruh keluarga rohani yang akan melipatganda untuk generasi-"
"generasi akan datang."

#: globals.php:2514
msgid "Great, Greater, and Greatest Blessing"
msgstr "Berkat Besar, Lebih Besar, dan Terbesar"

#: globals.php:2524 site/pages/follow-jesus.php:275
msgid "Duckling Discipleship – Leading Immediately"
msgstr "Pemuridan Anak Itik – Memimpin Dengan Segera"

#: globals.php:2526
msgid "Learn what ducklings have to do with disciple-making."
msgstr "Pelajari apa kaitannya anak itik dengan pemuridan."

#: globals.php:2527 site/course/course-content.php:1238
#: site/course/course-content.php:1357 site/course/course-content.php:1366
#: site/course/course-content.php:1519 site/course/course-content.php:4529
#: site/course/course-content.php:4550
msgid "Duckling Discipleship"
msgstr "Pemuridan Anak Itik"

#: globals.php:2537 globals.php:2540 site/course/course-content.php:1239
#: site/course/course-content.php:1405 site/course/course-content.php:1414
#: site/course/course-content.php:1520 site/course/course-content.php:4530
#: site/course/course-content.php:4551 site/pages/follow-jesus.php:256
msgid "Eyes to See Where the Kingdom Isn’t"
msgstr "Mata untuk Melihat Di Mana Kerajaan Tuhan Belum Hadir"

#: globals.php:2539 site/pages/follow-jesus.php:257
msgid ""
"Begin to see where God’s Kingdom isn’t. These are usually the places where "
"God wants to work the most."
msgstr ""
"Mulailah melihat di mana Kerajaan Tuhan belum hadir. Tempat-tempat inilah "
"yang biasanya menjadi tumpuan di mana Tuhan paling ingin bekerja."

#: globals.php:2550 site/pages/follow-jesus.php:241
msgid "The Lord’s Supper and How To Lead It"
msgstr "Perjamuan Tuhan dan Cara Memimpinnya"

#: globals.php:2552
msgid ""
"It’s a simple way to celebrate our intimate connection and ongoing "
"relationship with Jesus. Learn a simple way to celebrate."
msgstr ""
"Ia adalah cara yang ringkas untuk merayakan hubungan akrab dan berterusan "
"kita dengan Yesus. Pelajarilah cara yang mudah untuk merayakannya."

#: globals.php:2553 site/activities/activities.php:258
#: site/course/course-content.php:1244 site/course/course-content.php:1455
#: site/course/course-content.php:1464 site/course/course-content.php:1525
#: site/course/course-content.php:4534 site/course/course-content.php:4555
msgid "The Lord’s Supper"
msgstr "Perjamuan Tuhan"

#: globals.php:2563 site/pages/follow-jesus.php:313
msgid "Prayer Walking and How To Do It"
msgstr "Doa Sambil Berjalan dan Cara Melakukannya"

#: globals.php:2565
msgid ""
"It‘s a simple way to obey God’s command to pray for others. And it‘s just "
"what it sounds like — praying to God while walking around!"
msgstr ""
"Ia adalah cara yang ringkas untuk mentaati perintah Tuhan supaya mendoakan "
"orang lain. Ia sama seperti namanya — berdoa kepada Tuhan sambil berjalan-"
"jalan!"

#: globals.php:2566 site/activities/activities.php:327
#: site/course/course-content.php:1636 site/course/course-content.php:1644
#: site/course/course-content.php:1653 site/course/course-content.php:1759
#: site/course/course-content.php:4661 site/course/course-content.php:4674
msgid "Prayer Walking"
msgstr "Doa Sambil Berjalan"

#: globals.php:2576 site/pages/follow-jesus.php:309
msgid "A Person of Peace and How To Find One"
msgstr "Orang Damai Sejahtera dan Cara Mencari Mereka"

#: globals.php:2578
msgid ""
"Learn who a person of peace might be and how to know when you‘ve found one."
msgstr ""
"Pelajari siapa yang mungkin menjadi Orang Damai Sejahtera dan bagaimana "
"untuk mengetahui apabila anda telah menemui mereka."

#: globals.php:2579 site/course/course-content.php:1631
#: site/course/course-content.php:1676 site/course/course-content.php:1685
#: site/course/course-content.php:4777 site/course/course-content.php:4797
msgid "Person of Peace"
msgstr "Orang Damai"

#: globals.php:2589 site/pages/follow-jesus.php:222
msgid "Faithfulness is Better Than Knowledge"
msgstr "Ketaatan Lebih Baik Daripada Pengetahuan"

#: globals.php:2591
msgid ""
"It‘s important what disciples know — but it‘s much more important what they "
"DO with what they know."
msgstr ""
"Memang penting untuk seorang murid mempunyai pengetahuan — tetapi adalah "
"jauh lebih penting tentang apa yang mereka LAKUKAN dengan pengetahuan "
"tersebut."

#: globals.php:2592 site/course/course-content.php:1891
#: site/course/course-content.php:1900 site/course/course-content.php:4908
#: site/course/course-content.php:4957
msgid "Faithfulness"
msgstr "Kesetiaan"

#: globals.php:2602 site/pages/follow-jesus.php:211
msgid "The BLESS Prayer Pattern"
msgstr "Corak Doa BLESS"

#: globals.php:2604 site/pages/follow-jesus.php:212
msgid "Practice a simple mnemonic to remind you of ways to pray for others."
msgstr ""
"Praktikkan satu mnemonik mudah untuk mengingati cara-cara mendoakan orang "
"lain."

#: globals.php:2605 site/course/course-content.php:1725
msgid "The B.L.E.S.S. Prayer"
msgstr "Pola Doa B.L.E.S.S"

#: globals.php:2615 site/pages/follow-jesus.php:229
msgid "3/3 Group Meeting Pattern"
msgstr "Pola Perjumpaan Kumpulan 3/3"

#: globals.php:2617
msgid ""
"A 3/3 Group is a way for followers of Jesus to meet, pray, learn, grow, "
"fellowship and practice obeying and sharing what they‘ve learned. In this "
"way, a 3/3 Group is not just a small group but a Simple Church."
msgstr ""
"Kumpulan 3/3 adalah satu cara bagi pengikut Yesus untuk bertemu, berdoa, "
"belajar, berkembang, bersekutu dan berlatih mentaati serta mengongsikan apa "
"yang telah mereka pelajari. Dengan cara ini, Kumpulan 3/3 bukan sekadar "
"kumpulan kecil tetapi sebuah Gereja Sederhana."

#: globals.php:2618
msgid "3/3 Group"
msgstr "Kumpulan 3/3"

#: globals.php:2628 site/pages/follow-jesus.php:279
msgid "Training Cycle for Maturing Disciples"
msgstr "Kitaran Latihan untuk Murid yang Matang"

#: globals.php:2630 site/pages/follow-jesus.php:280
msgid ""
"Learn the training cycle and consider how it applies to disciple making."
msgstr ""
"Pelajari Kitaran Latihan dan pertimbangkan bagaimana ia diaplikasikan dalam "
"proses pembuatan murid."

#: globals.php:2631 site/course/course-content.php:5214
#: site/course/course-content.php:5231
msgid "Training Cycle"
msgstr "Kitaran Latihan"

#: globals.php:2641 globals.php:2644 site/course/course-content.php:2327
#: site/course/course-content.php:2339 site/course/course-content.php:2348
#: site/course/course-content.php:2421 site/course/course-content.php:5215
#: site/course/course-content.php:5232 site/pages/follow-jesus.php:334
msgid "Leadership Cells"
msgstr "Sel Kepimpinan"

#: globals.php:2643 site/course/course-content.php:2350
#: site/pages/follow-jesus.php:335
msgid ""
"A Leadership Cell is a way someone who feels called to lead can develop "
"their leadership by practicing serving."
msgstr ""
"Sel Kepimpinan adalah satu cara bagi seseorang yang merasa terpanggil untuk "
"memimpin bagi mengembangkan kepimpinan mereka dengan berlatih melayani."

#: globals.php:2654 globals.php:2657 site/course/course-content.php:5339
#: site/course/course-content.php:5357 site/pages/follow-jesus.php:283
msgid "Expect Non-Sequential Growth"
msgstr "Jangkakan Pertumbuhan Bukan Berurutan"

#: globals.php:2656
msgid ""
"See how disciple making doesn‘t have to be linear. Multiple things can "
"happen at the same time."
msgstr ""
"Lihat bagaimana proses pembuatan murid tidak semestinya bersifat linear "
"(lurus). Pelbagai perkara boleh berlaku dalam masa yang sama."

#: globals.php:2667 site/course/course-content.php:2930
#: site/pages/follow-jesus.php:287
msgid "Pace of Multiplication Matters"
msgstr "Kelajuan Pelipatgandaan Adalah Penting"

#: globals.php:2669 site/pages/follow-jesus.php:288
msgid ""
"Multiplying matters and multiplying quickly matters even more. See why pace "
"matters."
msgstr ""
"Pelipatgandaan itu penting, dan melipatganda dengan pantas adalah jauh lebih "
"penting. Lihat mengapa kelajuan itu amat bermakna."

#: globals.php:2670 site/course/course-content.php:2532
#: site/course/course-content.php:2595 site/course/course-content.php:2604
#: site/course/course-content.php:5340 site/course/course-content.php:5358
msgid "Pace"
msgstr "Kelajuan"

#: globals.php:2680 globals.php:2683 site/course/course-content.php:2533
#: site/course/course-content.php:2644 site/course/course-content.php:2653
#: site/course/course-content.php:2931 site/course/course-content.php:5341
#: site/course/course-content.php:5359 site/pages/follow-jesus.php:237
msgid "Always Part of Two Churches"
msgstr "Sentiasa Menjadi Bahagian daripada Dua Gereja"

#: globals.php:2682
msgid "Learn how to obey Jesus‘ commands by going AND staying."
msgstr "Pelajari cara mentaati perintah Yesus dengan pergi DAN tinggal."

#: globals.php:2694 globals.php:2697 site/course/course-content.php:3062
