#: site/pages/about.php:211
msgid "Before you start."
msgstr "Sebelum anda bermula."

#: site/pages/about.php:218
msgid "Zúme is NOT like other trainings!"
msgstr "Zúme TIDAK sama seperti latihan-latihan lain!"

#: site/pages/about.php:220
msgid "First:"
msgstr "Pertama:"

#: site/pages/about.php:221
msgid ""
"Zúme is designed to be done as a group. Group exercise, discussions, and "
"practicing of skills all will be better with others, so gather a group, if "
"possible."
msgstr ""
"Zúme direka untuk dilakukan secara berkumpulan. Latihan kumpulan, "
"perbincangan, dan mempraktikkan kemahiran, semuanya akan menjadi lebih baik "
"bersama orang lain; jadi, kumpulkan satu kumpulan jika boleh."

#: site/pages/about.php:224
msgid "Second:"
msgstr "Kedua:"

#: site/pages/about.php:225
msgid ""
"Zúme is about developing skills, building competence, not just gaining "
"knowledge . In every session, the goal is fruitful action. The best outcome "
"of the training will be a changed lifestyle and an experience of increased "
"power in your faith."
msgstr ""
"Zúme adalah mengenai membangunkan kemahiran dan membina kecekapan, bukan "
"sekadar menimba pengetahuan. Dalam setiap sesi, matlamatnya adalah tindakan "
"yang membuahkan hasil. Hasil terbaik daripada latihan ini adalah gaya hidup "
"yang berubah dan pengalaman peningkatan kuasa dalam iman anda."

#: site/pages/about.php:233
msgid "What's required"
msgstr "Apakah yang diperlukan"

#: site/pages/about.php:236
msgid "Needed for the training:"
msgstr "Diperlukan untuk latihan ini:"

#: site/pages/about.php:238 site/pages/training.php:266
msgid "At least 3 people, but ideally less than 12."
msgstr ""
"Sekurang-kurangnya 3 orang, tetapi sebaik-baiknya kurang daripada 12 orang."

#: site/pages/about.php:239 site/pages/training.php:267
msgid ""
"Commitment to spend 20 hours learning and practicing the concepts and tools "
"in the course."
msgstr ""
"Komitmen untuk meluangkan 20 jam bagi mempelajari dan mempraktikkan konsep "
"serta alat dalam kursus ini."

#: site/pages/about.php:240 site/pages/training.php:268
msgid ""
"A person to facilitate (potentially you) the meeting time and location, to "
"guide the follow-up discussion, and facilitate action prompts."
msgstr ""
"Seseorang untuk menjadi fasilitator (mungkin anda) bagi masa dan lokasi "
"pertemuan, untuk membimbing perbincangan susulan, serta memudah cara "
"tindakan yang perlu diambil."

#: site/pages/about.php:249
msgid "NOT needed for the training:"
msgstr "TIDAK diperlukan untuk latihan ini:"

#: site/pages/about.php:251 site/pages/training.php:272
msgid ""
"More knowledge or experience than the rest of your group is not needed! If "
"you can click next, you can lead a Zúme Training."
msgstr ""
"Anda tidak perlu mempunyai lebih banyak pengetahuan atau pengalaman "
"berbanding ahli kumpulan anda yang lain! Jika anda boleh menekan butang "
"seterusnya, anda mampu memimpin Latihan Zúme."

#: site/pages/about.php:252
msgid ""
"Special permission to lead a training is not needed! Zúme is self-"
"facilitated, self-initiated, and you can start today."
msgstr ""
"Tidak perlukan kebenaran khas untuk memimpin latihan ini! Zúme diuruskan "
"sendiri, dimulakan sendiri, dan anda boleh bermula hari ini."

#: site/pages/about.php:263
msgid "Connecting with a Coach."
msgstr "Berhubung dengan Seorang Jurulatih."

#: site/pages/about.php:270
msgid ""
"All along the way, the Zúme community is eager to support you by providing a "
"COACH to help you and your group successfully implement the training. Don’t "
"hesitate to reach out with questions or concerns!"
msgstr ""
"Sepanjang perjalanan ini, komuniti Zúme sangat bersemangat untuk menyokong "
"anda dengan menyediakan JURULATIH untuk membantu anda dan kumpulan anda "
"melaksanakan latihan ini dengan berjaya. Jangan teragak-agak untuk "
"menghubungi kami jika mempunyai sebarang soalan atau kebimbangan!"

