#: site/pages/follow-jesus.php:223
msgid ""
"It's important what disciples know — but it's much more important what they "
"DO with what they know."
msgstr ""
"Adalah penting untuk mengetahui apa yang diketahui oleh setiap murid — "
"tetapi jauh lebih penting adalah apa yang mereka LAKUKAN dengan apa yang "
"mereka ketahui."

#: site/pages/follow-jesus.php:230
msgid ""
"A 3/3 Group is a way for followers of Jesus to meet, pray, learn, grow, "
"fellowship and practice obeying and sharing what they've learned. In this "
"way, a 3/3 Group is not just a small group but a Simple Church."
msgstr ""
"Kumpulan 3/3 merupakan satu cara untuk pengikut Yesus bertemu, berdoa, "
"belajar, bertumbuh, bersekutu, serta mempraktikkan ketaatan dan berkongsi "
"apa yang telah dipelajari. Dengan cara ini, Kumpulan 3/3 bukan sekadar "
"kumpulan kecil, tetapi sebuah Gereja Ringkas."

#: site/pages/follow-jesus.php:238
msgid "Learn how to obey Jesus' commands by going AND staying."
msgstr ""
"Pelajari cara untuk mentaati perintah Yesus dengan cara pergi DAN tinggal."

#: site/pages/follow-jesus.php:242
msgid ""
"It's a simple way to celebrate our intimate connection and ongoing "
"relationship with Jesus. Learn a simple way to celebrate."
msgstr ""
"Ini adalah cara yang mudah untuk meraikan hubungan intim dan hubungan "
"berterusan kita dengan Yesus. Pelajari cara yang mudah untuk meraikan."

#: site/pages/follow-jesus.php:250
msgid "Sacrifice and Suffering"
msgstr "Pengorbanan dan Penderitaan"

#: site/pages/follow-jesus.php:264
msgid "How do I obey Jesus and help others become followers with me?"
msgstr ""
"Bagaimanakah saya mentaati Yesus dan membantu orang lain menjadi pengikut "
"bersama saya?"

#: site/pages/follow-jesus.php:269
msgid ""
"Then Jesus came to them and said, \"All authority in heaven and on earth has "
"been given to me. Therefore go and make disciples of all nations, baptizing "
"them in the name of the Father and of the Son and of the Holy Spirit, and "
"teaching them to obey everything I have commanded you. And surely I am with "
"you always, to the very end of the age.\""
msgstr ""
"Lalu Yesus menghampiri mereka dan berkata, \"Segala kuasa di syurga dan di "
"bumi telah diberikan kepada-Ku. Oleh itu, pergilah, jadikan semua bangsa "
"murid-Ku, baptislah mereka dalam nama Bapa, Anak, dan Roh Kudus, serta "
"ajarlah mereka mentaati segala sesuatu yang telah Aku perintahkan kepadamu. "
"Dan ketahuilah, Aku menyertai kamu senantiasa, sampai akhir zaman.\""

#: site/pages/follow-jesus.php:270
msgid "Matthew 28:18-20"
msgstr "Matius 28:18-20"

