#: site/pages/privacy-policy.php:29 site/pages/privacy-policy.php:86
msgid "Zúme Privacy Policy"
msgstr "Dasar Privasi Zúme"

#: site/pages/privacy-policy.php:88
msgid ""
"This privacy policy has been compiled to better serve those who are "
"concerned with how their \"Personally Identifiable Information\" (PII) is "
"being used online. PII, as described in US privacy law and information "
"security, is information that can be used on its own or with other "
"information to identify, contact, or locate a single person, or to identify "
"an individual in context. Please read our privacy policy carefully to get a "
"clear understanding of how we collect, use, protect or otherwise handle your "
"Personally Identifiable Information in accordance with our website."
msgstr ""
"Dasar privasi ini telah digubal untuk memberi perkhidmatan yang lebih baik "
"kepada mereka yang bimbang tentang bagaimana \"Maklumat Pengenalan "
"Peribadi\" (PII) mereka digunakan dalam talian. PII, seperti yang "
"diterangkan dalam undang-undang privasi dan keselamatan maklumat AS, ialah "
"maklumat yang boleh digunakan secara sendirian atau dengan maklumat lain "
"untuk mengenal pasti, menghubungi, atau mencari seseorang individu, atau "
"untuk mengenal pasti seseorang individu dalam konteks. Sila baca dasar "
"privasi kami dengan teliti untuk mendapatkan pemahaman yang jelas tentang "
"cara kami mengumpul, menggunakan, melindungi, atau mengendalikan Maklumat "
"Pengenalan Peribadi anda selaras dengan laman web kami."

#: site/pages/privacy-policy.php:92
msgid "What permissions do the social sign-on logins ask for?"
msgstr "Apakah keizinan yang diminta oleh daftar masuk sosial?"

#: site/pages/privacy-policy.php:93
msgid ""
"The profile elements below change depending on if Facebook or Google sign on "
"is used."
msgstr ""
"Elemen profil di bawah berubah bergantung kepada sama ada daftar masuk "
"Facebook atau Google digunakan."

#: site/pages/privacy-policy.php:96
msgid ""
"Public Profile. This includes certain User’s Data such as id, name, picture, "
"gender, and their locale."
msgstr ""
"Profil Awam. Ini merangkumi Data Pengguna tertentu seperti id, nama, gambar, "
"jantina, dan lokasi mereka."

#: site/pages/privacy-policy.php:99
msgid "Email Address."
msgstr "Alamat E-mel."

#: site/pages/privacy-policy.php:106
msgid ""
"What personal information do we collect from the people through our website?"
msgstr ""
"Apakah maklumat peribadi yang kami kumpul daripada orang ramai melalui laman "
"web kami?"

#: site/pages/privacy-policy.php:107
msgid ""
"Some personal information is tracked for the proper functioning of the "
"website, and other information is requested and saved for additional "
"coaching and support."
msgstr ""
"Sebahagian maklumat peribadi dijejaki untuk kefungsian laman web yang betul, "
"manakala maklumat lain diminta dan disimpan untuk tujuan bimbingan dan "
"sokongan tambahan."

#: site/pages/privacy-policy.php:129
msgid "When do we collect information?"
msgstr "Bilakah kami mengumpul maklumat?"

#: site/pages/privacy-policy.php:132
msgid "We collect your information at login."
msgstr "Kami mengumpul maklumat anda semasa daftar masuk."

#: site/pages/privacy-policy.php:135
msgid ""
"We also track your progress through the training course and through site "
"usage."
msgstr ""
"Kami juga menjejaki kemajuan anda melalui kursus latihan dan melalui "
"penggunaan laman web."

#: site/pages/privacy-policy.php:138
msgid ""
"We request neccissary information through various sign up and request forms."
msgstr ""
"Kami meminta maklumat yang diperlukan melalui pelbagai borang pendaftaran "
"dan permintaan."

#: site/pages/privacy-policy.php:145
msgid "How do we use your information?"
msgstr "Bagaimanakah kami menggunakan maklumat anda?"

#: site/pages/privacy-policy.php:148
msgid ""
"We use your information to create a user account in the zume system based on "
"your email address."
msgstr ""
"Kami menggunakan maklumat anda untuk mencipta akaun pengguna dalam sistem "
"Zúme berdasarkan alamat e-mel anda."

#: site/pages/privacy-policy.php:151
msgid ""
"We will email you with basic transactional emails like password reset "
"requests and other system notifications."
msgstr ""
"Kami akan menghantar e-mel kepada anda dengan e-mel transaksi asas seperti "
"permintaan tetapan semula kata laluan dan pemberitahuan sistem yang lain."

#: site/pages/privacy-policy.php:154
msgid ""
"We email occasional reminders and encouragements depending on your progress "
"through the training."
msgstr ""
"Kami menghantar peringatan dan kata-kata semangat secara berkala bergantung "
"kepada kemajuan anda melalui latihan tersebut."

#: site/pages/privacy-policy.php:161
msgid "How do we protect your information?"
msgstr "Bagaimanakah kami melindungi maklumat anda?"

#: site/pages/privacy-policy.php:163
msgid ""
"While we use encryption to protect sensitive information transmitted online, "
"we also protect your information offline. Only team members who need the "
"information to perform a specific job (for example, web administrator or "
"customer service) are granted access to personally identifiable information."
msgstr ""
"Walaupun kami menggunakan penyulitan untuk melindungi maklumat sensitif yang "
"dihantar dalam talian, kami juga melindungi maklumat anda di luar talian. "
"Hanya ahli pasukan yang memerlukan maklumat tersebut untuk melaksanakan "
"tugas tertentu (contohnya, pentadbir web atau khidmat pelanggan) diberikan "
"akses kepada maklumat pengenalan peribadi."

#: site/pages/privacy-policy.php:166
msgid ""
"Your personal information is contained behind secured networks and is only "
"accessible by a limited number of persons who have special access rights to "
"such systems, and are required to keep the information confidential. In "
"addition, all sensitive/credit information you supply is encrypted via "
"Secure Socket Layer (SSL) technology."
msgstr ""
"Maklumat peribadi anda disimpan di sebalik rangkaian yang selamat dan hanya "
"boleh diakses oleh sebilangan kecil individu yang mempunyai hak akses khas "
"kepada sistem tersebut, dan mereka diwajibkan untuk menyimpan maklumat "
"tersebut secara sulit. Selain itu, semua maklumat sensitif/kredit yang anda "
"bekalkan disulitkan melalui teknologi Secure Socket Layer (SSL)."

#: site/pages/privacy-policy.php:169
msgid ""
"We implement a variety of security measures when a user submits, or accesses "
"their information to maintain the safety of your personal information."
msgstr ""
"Kami melaksanakan pelbagai langkah keselamatan apabila pengguna menghantar "
"atau mengakses maklumat mereka bagi mengekalkan keselamatan maklumat "
"peribadi anda."

#: site/pages/privacy-policy.php:175
msgid "Do we use \"cookies\"?"
msgstr "Adakah kami menggunakan cookies?"

#: site/pages/privacy-policy.php:177
msgid ""
"Any use of Cookies - or of other tracking tools - unless stated otherwise, "
"serves to identify Users and remember their preferences, for the sole "
"purpose of providing the service required by the User."
msgstr ""
"Sebarang penggunaan Coookies – atau alat penjejakan lain – melainkan "
"dinyatakan sebaliknya, bertujuan untuk mengenal pasti Pengguna dan "
"mengingati pilihan mereka, semata-mata untuk tujuan menyediakan perkhidmatan "
"yang diperlukan oleh Pengguna."

#: site/pages/privacy-policy.php:183
msgid "Your Access to and Control Over Information."
msgstr "Akses dan Kawalan Anda Terhadap Maklumat."

#: site/pages/privacy-policy.php:185
msgid ""
"You can do the following at any time by contacting us via our \"Get a "
"Coach\" form and choosing \"Technical Assistance\" from your user dashboard."
msgstr ""
"Anda boleh melakukan perkara berikut pada bila-bila masa dengan menghubungi "
"kami melalui borang \"Dapatkan Jurulatih\" dan memilih \"Bantuan Teknikal\" "
"daripada papan pemuka pengguna anda."

#: site/pages/privacy-policy.php:190
msgid "See what data we've aggregated from your activities with us."
msgstr ""
"Lihat data yang telah kami kumpulkan daripada aktiviti anda bersama kami."

#: site/pages/privacy-policy.php:193
msgid "Change/correct any data we have about you."
msgstr "Ubah/betulkan sebarang data yang kami miliki tentang anda."

#: site/pages/privacy-policy.php:196
msgid "Have us delete your account or any data we have about you."
msgstr ""
"Minta kami memadamkan akaun anda atau sebarang data yang kami miliki tentang "
"anda."

#: site/pages/privacy-policy.php:199
msgid "Express any concern you have about our use of your data."
msgstr ""
"Nyatakan sebarang kebimbangan yang anda miliki tentang penggunaan data anda "
"oleh kami."

#: site/pages/privacy-policy.php:202
msgid "Opt out of any future contact from us."
msgstr ""
"Berhenti daripada menerima sebarang hubungan pada masa hadapan daripada kami."

#: site/pages/privacy-policy.php:209
msgid "Updates"
msgstr "Kemas Kini"

#: site/pages/privacy-policy.php:211
msgid ""
